          "displayName": "Bikas Saha",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
        },
        "body": "When does MR use multiple disks in the same task/container? Isnt the map output written to a single indexed partition file?\n\nRequiring apps to specify the number of disks for a container is also a viable solution and can be done in a back-compatible manner by changing MR to specify multiple disks and leaving the default to 1 for apps that dont care.",
